products.name: Subaru WRX
products.description: The all-new 2022 Subaru WRX is here to take rally-born, high-performance driving further than ever before, with a new, more powerful turbocharged SUBARU BOXER engine, an upgraded track-tuned suspension, the legendary grip of Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, and a resculpted, athletic exterior that takes inspiration from its championship motorsport heritage with an eye to the future. The WRX represents decades of rally racing experience translated and re-engineered for unleashed power, precision handling, and thrilling performance.

products.name: Subaru Outback
products.description: Designed for unlimited adventure and uncompromising safety, the 2022 Outback features the confidence of standard Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive with up to 33 MPG** and the advanced protection of both standard EyeSight® Driver Assist Technology and the available DriverFocus® Distraction Mitigation System. And it’s engineered to last, with 97% of Outback vehicles sold in the last 10 years still on the road today. For 2022, an even higher level of Outback capability is now available: the all-new Subaru Outback Wilderness, featuring extensive all-terrain upgrades including an even more surefooted drivetrain, increased ground clearance, rugged exterior cladding, and a stylish, unique interior.

products.name: Toyota Tundra
products.description: Redesigned from the ground up and engineered for adventure, the 2022 Tundra is our toughest, most capable, most advanced Tundra to date.
